data.description: You Don't Want To Miss Seeing This Beautiful Two Story Townhouse in Hawks Point West with Water View and a Double car garage. Close to Apollo Beach with 4 bedrooms, 2 and 1/2 Bathrooms. Very Spacious and has a Beautiful Full View of the pond, birds, turtles... to watch. Enclosed Entry porch and Screened Back Lanai with beautiful tile. Crown Molding on the first floor which was recently painted, and Backsplash was added to the Kitchen. A Storage closet on the first floor is decorated into a cute pet room ."Barn Style" gate door was made for the entrance of the stairway to the second floor. The First Floor is an Open Living Space with High ceilings, a large kitchen, dining and living room. Granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Hurricane Shutters, Garage Ceiling Storage, outdoor garage lighting, garage tool peg boards, Laundry room shelving. Keypad entry door, pre-wired ADP Spectrum Cable. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms and living room. The location is excellent, very close to US 301 and I75 US 41 giving you access on any route, close to Schools, the Hillsborough Community College, and Amazon's Distribution Center. Close access to the Beaches, The Ellenton Prime Outlets, Manatee Viewing Center, EG Simmons Regional Park, Little Harbour Marinas and Resorts, and Restaurants with lots of entertainment around. Close to Tampa, Busch Gardens. St. Joseph Hospital, South Bay Hospital, Walmart, restaurants, Grocery Stores... Hawks Point is a Gated Community and a great place to live: playground, dog park, 2 pools, gym, Clubhouse, and nightly security patrolling. The ceiling fan in Lanai does not convey.
